# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  NEVER COMMIT THESE TO GITHUB (public repo) — see ../CLAUDE.md
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# (1) Licensed publisher graphics / game art — publisher IP, do NOT redistribute.
#     Lives locally and deploys to BGA via SFTP only.
#     (Force-add self-authored assets if ever needed: `git add -f path`)
img/

# (2) Credentials — never commit an SFTP/BGA password, token, or private key.
#     We use SSH-key auth; the local SFTP config stays out of git.
#     Commit only sftp.json.example (a key PATH, never a secret).
.vscode/sftp.json

# ── Local-only Claude settings (the rest of .claude/ IS tracked → GitHub) ──
.claude/settings.local.json

# ── Node / build tooling (package-lock.json IS tracked for reproducible builds) ──
node_modules/

# ── OS / editor cruft ──
Thumbs.db
.DS_Store
